### Goal
Build a provider-abstracted LLM gateway that routes requests to the correct provider, enforces access control, and logs every call.

### Supported Providers

{{#each providers_display}}
- **{{this.name}}** (`{{this.id}}`)
{{/each}}

### API Route

**POST `/api/llm/gateway`**

Request body:
```json
{
  "prompt_slug": "my-prompt-template",
  "variables": {
    "user_input": "Hello, world!"
  },
  "stream": false
}
```

Success response:
```json
